

=Bio=

"secretary general of CECOP CICOPA-Europe, European confederation of industrial and service cooperatives, and CICOPA, global organization of industrial and service cooperatives. Our cooperatives are of different types, the main ones being worker cooperatives, social cooperatives, individual producers’ / freelancers’ cooperatives, and mixed / multistakeholder cooperatives. Most platform cooperatives are in our cooperative sector. I am really interested in taking part in this conversation, and we are also interested to study platform cooperativism within the framework of the future of work."
(Loomio, January 2017)


